---
title: Chili-Garlic and Honey Tofu Wraps with Wedges and Creamy Dill Pickle Slaw
description: Tonight's veggie dinner features the sensational pairing of hot-honey sauce and cooling dill pickle flavours. Don't be scared to choose your own spice level, as you've got crispy coleslaw in every bite.
